          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bg-white">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Getting Started</h2>
      <div class="content-prose">
        <p>Send a photo of your certificate via WhatsApp. We will review it and tell you exactly what is needed: whether attestation is required, what the translation will cost, and how long it will take.</p>
        
        <p>If you are unsure which documents you need translated, describe your situation—what you are trying to accomplish—and we will advise on the complete documentation requirements. Whether it is a work permit, visa application, or professional license, we can guide you through the process.</p>
        
        <p>For multiple certificates or family packages, we provide combined pricing and coordinated processing. All certificates will be delivered together, properly sequenced for your submission.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

